# DSA Foundation

## What is Space Complexity?

Space Complexity measures the amount of additional memory an algorithm requires as the input size grows.

Examples

One Variable

```
O(1)
```

Additional Array of Size n

```
O(n)
```

---

# Industry Connection

When a user registers in our Hospital Management System:

```java
String patientName = "Rahul";

int age = 25;

boolean admitted = true;
```

Every piece of information is stored using variables and appropriate data types.

